      <title>
         <ph props="autonumber">204.1202</ph> Solicitation provision and contract clause.</title>
      <conbody>
         <p>When using the provision at <ph xtrc="FARxref">FAR 52.204-8</ph>, Annual Representations and Certifications—</p>
         <p outputclass="List2">(1) Use the provision with <ph xtrc="DFARxref">
